data_table.description: Data contain extensive medical history information of subjects (all > 65 years of age), describing general physical and psychological health, their use of medications/multivitamins, cognitive and emotional well being, and subjects' mobility/independence and movement limitations. Lifestyle information is provided through variables querying for exercise habits, smoking, and alcohol consumption. The data also include information about the family history of myocardial infarcts and stroke. Data were collected at baseline (1).
